{"id": 761, "genre": 1001, "title": "你为啥讨厌同学聚会？", "description": "上学的时候关系都没多好，隔了这么多年更没有什么好聊的。（题图来自：Yukai Du）", "record_count": 10373, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183655TAoUr0lMxqYR7GeD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-16T01:04:54Z", "options": [{"id": 45571, "content": "别说同学聚会，我有社恐，我妈都嫌弃死我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 41733, "content": "本来就不熟，好久都没见了，更不想见", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 322133}, {"id": 43013, "content": "没有能和我一醉方休的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434780}, {"id": 41734, "content": "去了也是个配角，还不如在自己世界里当主角", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182902MihjspAd2ZWtOy1V.jpg", "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390073}, {"id": 41990, "content": "大学同学其实还好，初中高中同学聚会其实现在变得越来越有分歧，长时间的不见面，再加上工作上接触的差别，见面不知道要说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292804}, {"id": 41991, "content": "我的同学，只要一毕业就，都死了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237498}, {"id": 42247, "content": "会遇到前男友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428382}, {"id": 41480, "content": "没有喜欢的人 同什么学会", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416583}, {"id": 41992, "content": "为什么为啥你们不喜欢同学会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428187}, {"id": 41481, "content": "假高尚，真虚伪……", "image": null, "praise_count": 192, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68366}, {"id": 41482, "content": "因为只有我从那时候开始到现在就没有长过身高，?不想去丢脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324550}, {"id": 41994, "content": "因为每次都得我去组织", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428202}, {"id": 45322, "content": "自卑感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449162}, {"id": 46090, "content": "人都变化太大 无话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326735}, {"id": 41483, "content": "圈子不同，何必强融", "image": null, "praise_count": 525, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92636}, {"id": 89356, "content": "活在当下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647500}, {"id": 41484, "content": "暂时还不讨厌，虽然不会聊天，但是坐在角落看看大家也挺好的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 45836, "content": "宁愿和一群陌生人坐在一起也不要去同学聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451945}, {"id": 63756, "content": "一走进去大家都望着你的那一刻真的很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547945}, {"id": 41485, "content": "明明当年关系不咋样，见了面还得说：当初咱俩玩的多好啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 131, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410221}, {"id": 41997, "content": "虽有同学之实，并无同窗之情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428199}, {"id": 45326, "content": "因为看到以前很喜欢的人还是会心动?，感觉很不自在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449124}, {"id": 41487, "content": "我比以前胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425095}, {"id": 42255, "content": "见到就烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429459}, {"id": 41488, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 416, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311396}, {"id": 41489, "content": "难得的约炮机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 41490, "content": "文科班当年各种小团体与内斗，N年过去还是如此。文科男只能在一旁默默地看看，笑笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331863}, {"id": 41491, "content": "同学会=应酬", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309899}, {"id": 42259, "content": "我脸盲记不住人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429521}, {"id": 41492, "content": "人生百态 处处可见  偶尔聚聚何必太在意", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425113}, {"id": 44052, "content": "烦感被问到挣多少，自己却暗暗的想知道别人的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422421}, {"id": 41493, "content": "发现几年下来，水平都太差，聊天非口水，不是精神活动的需求.", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425110}, {"id": 41494, "content": "见见他们怀念一下青春，然后退出同学微信群。连跟初恋约炮的兴趣也没有。好吧，其实我跟你们没有什么感情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403}, {"id": 42006, "content": "没啥就是不想被你们发现这么多年过去了我还是这么丑……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351780}, {"id": 41495, "content": "还是话当年", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66019}, {"id": 41496, "content": "沉默过度", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345601}, {"id": 43288, "content": "生活的圈子不一样了，没有共同语言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436502}, {"id": 41497, "content": "不讨厌啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 42009, "content": "虽然隔阂众多、但毕竟当年有缘成为同窗、聚一聚也是不错的（有些事不用看的看复杂就好，不过是一场单纯的聚会）", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200845q8Vkov01rTH934Kh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278400}, {"id": 41499, "content": "就是不想去", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 41500, "content": "主要是关系不到位，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307916}, {"id": 42012, "content": "物是人非", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344781}, {"id": 41501, "content": "差异感会随着时间渐渐显露，不再是当年的感觉，不再是当年的模样，即使以前的事情仿佛还历历在目，但是人走茶凉，之后各是各的世界，往事不需重提，向前看依然是美好人生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 424959}, {"id": 41502, "content": "真正关系好的 时常都在聚 关系不好的 多说句话都觉得虚伪", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400490}, {"id": 41503, "content": "还没有到要靠回忆支撑生活的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200116}, {"id": 44831, "content": "次数太多 无意义", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446034}, {"id": 41504, "content": "喜欢同学聚会的无非几类人，有钱想炫耀，有情想续上，有事想求人。如果不是，我去那干啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 404, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411875}, {"id": 41760, "content": "除了攀比还是攀比，主要是自己没什么可炫耀的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426901}, {"id": 44832, "content": "每次看老师看老师看老师老师都被看烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446034}, {"id": 41505, "content": "圈子不同 何必强求", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423271}]}